tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VolunteerEngagementData (
    volunteer_id INT,
    volunteer_name TEXT,
    engagement_date DATE,
    hours_volunteered FLOAT,
    project_name TEXT,
    volunteer_role TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (volunteer_id)
)

CREATE TABLE volunteers (
    volunteer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE volunteer_activity (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    volunteer_id INT,
    activity_name VARCHAR(50),
    date_started DATE,
    date_completed DATE,
    hours_spent FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (volunteer_id) REFERENCES volunteers(volunteer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE volunteers (
    volunteer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    phone_number VARCHAR,
    address VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE volunteer_activities (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_name VARCHAR,
    volunteer_id INT,
    activity_date DATE,
    hours_spent FLOAT,
    engagement_level INT
);

CREATE TABLE Participation (
    participation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    volunteer_id INT,
    activity_id INT,
    participation_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (volunteer_id) REFERENCES Volunteer(volunteer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (activity_id) REFERENCES Activity(activity_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participation_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (participation_id) REFERENCES Participation(participation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE volunteers (
    volunteer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    phone_number VARCHAR,
    join_date DATE
);
